Package se.controller

se.controller contains Servlets using MVC model and other common classes for usage within the Servlets.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    agdServlet
    The servlet that does processing for the Automatic Group Detection
    BootstrapServlet
    The servlet that performs bootstrapping of the file.
    demographicServlet
    The servlet that does processing for breakdown by year and gender
    FileValidation
    The class containing common methods for validation of the different files
    HeatmapServlet
    The servlet that processes the data for the heatmap function
    LoginServlet
    The servlet that processes user Login
    ReadCSV
    Does reading of the csv files
    TopKCServlet
    The servlet that processes the data for Top K Companions
    TopKNPServlet
    The servlet that processes data for Top K Next Places
    TopKPPServlet
    The servlet that processes data for Top K Popular Places
    UpdateServlet
    The servlet that processes the file update for new files
    uploadServlet
    The servlet that does unziping and processing for files to be bootstrapped
    UploadUpdateServlet
    The servlet that does unziping and processing for new files to update the database
    Validate
    Contains methods for validation of fields within the different csv files
    WriteCSV
    Performs writing of validated rows into csv

Package se.controller Description

se.controller contains Servlets using MVC model and other common classes for usage within the Servlets.
